Class Tournament

  • java.lang.Object
    • game.Tournament

  • public class Tournament
extends java.lang.Object
    Just replace add whatever players you want to participate in the tournament to the players list. Make sure no two players have the same name or else the scores will come out wrong. Scores at the end are printed out in no particular order.
